omy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-gst-collections-increase-10-to-rs-1-75-trillion-in-august-124090100462_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-gst-collections-increase-10-to-rs-1-75-trillion-in-august-124090100462_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Investors%20are%20headed%20into%20the%20worst%20time%20of%20year%20for%20stocks.%20Here's%20why%20September%20is%20brutal%20for%20the%20market.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bear%20with%20a%20speech%20bubble%20showing%20a%20downward%20stock%20arrow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d20dc71d8d2deb96b7d65f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAdobe%20Firefly%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20a%20history%20of%20underperforming%20in%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EVolatility%20rises%20in%20the%20month%20as%20traders%20reposition%20their%20portfolios.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESeveral%20market-moving%20events%20could%20make%20this%20September%20especially%20unique.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20August%20closes%20out%20the%20summer%20season%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%3Futm_source%3Dmarkets%26utm_medium%3Dingest%253Futm_source%253Dmarkets%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20soon%20take%20its%20own%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20September%20has%20been%20the%20worst%20month%20for%20the%20benchmark%20index%20going%20back%20as%20far%20as%201928.%20Not%20only%20do%20stocks%20regularly%20underperform%2C%20it's%20also%20not%20unusual%20for%20the%20market%20to%20end%20the%20month%20with%20a%20negative%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fopenmarkets%2Fequity-index%2F2023%2Fthree-reasons-for-the-September-Effect-in-stocks.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECME%20Group%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20last%20year%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20lost%20ground%20in%2055%25%20of%20Septembers%20over%20the%20the%20last%20century.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20index%20has%20dropped%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-crash-selloff-outlook-august-fed-rates-geopolitics-inflation-jobs-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeutsche%20Bank%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20culprit%20is%20the%20higher%20trading%20volumes%20as%20Wall%20Street%20gets%20back%20to%20work%20after%20Labor%20Day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20traders%20out%20on%20vacation%20during%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20stock%20activity%20tends%20to%20lag%2C%20resulting%20in%20stronger%20market%20performance%20amid%20thinner%20trading%20volumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoFi's%20Liz%20Young%20Thomas%20noted%20that%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20monthly%20trading%20volumes%20average%2015.2%20billion%20shares%20between%20June%20and%20August.%20But%20when%20investors%20return%20to%20their%20desks%20in%20September%2C%20volume%20jumps%20to%2017.2%20billion%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20coming%20back%20in%20and%20starting%20to%20trade%20again.%20You've%20just%20got%20more%20activity%20in%20the%20market%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20volatility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20head%20of%20investment%20strategy%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BJust%20naturally%2C%20people%20might%20take%20a%20look%20at%20portfolios%20and%20say%3A%20'I'm%20a%20little%20overweight%20the%20Mag%20Seven%2C%20or%20I'm%20a%20little%20overweight%20large-cap%20equity%2C%20or%20I'm%20just%20overweight%20equity%20in%20general.''%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeptember%20experiences%20some%20of%20the%20year's%20most%20volatile%20swings%2C%20and%202%25%20moves%20in%20either%20direction%20are%20a%20norm%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20she%20said.%20Although%20volatility%20continues%20through%20the%20fall%2C%20September%20stands%20out%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20downside%20swings%20widely%20outweigh%20upside%20momentum%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22599b94c5-c372-4d68-84a2-1ad6e475f211%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20expect%20this%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20market-moving%20events%20could%20make%20this%20September%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20policy%20meeting%20on%20September%2018.%20Interest%20rate%20cuts%20are%20widely%20expected%2C%20a%20move%20that's%20generally%20framed%20as%20positive%20for%20the%20bull%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20LPL%20Financial's%20Adam%20Turnquist%2C%20this%20could%20shift%20based%20on%20the%20upcoming%20August%20jobs%20report%20due%20out%20on%20September%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20labor%20print%20is%20weaker%20than%20expected%2C%20the%20Fed%20might%20pursue%20deeper%20rate%20cuts%2C%20which%20would%20be%20an%20acknowledgment%20of%20a%20weakening%20economy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20event%20we%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20better%20economic%20data%20next%20week%2C%20the%20soft%20landing%20narrative%20gains%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20momentum%2C%20and%20we%20potentially%20buck%20the%20losing%20streak%20we've%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20technical%20strategist%20Adam%20Turnquist%20told%20BI%2C%20but%20outlined%20that%20downside%20risk%20looks%20more%20probable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20September%2C%20election%20jitters%20can%20only%20extend%20seasonal%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoFi's%20Young%20Thomas%20noted%20that%20heightened%20volatility%20peaks%20in%20mid-October%20during%20election%20years%2C%20not%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that's%20frequently%20followed%20by%20a%20relief%20rally%20once%20the%20results%20are%20known%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20prepare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortfolios%20shouldn't%20be%20readjusted%20because%20of%20seasonal%20shakiness%2C%20each%20expert%20told%20BI%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20both%20hard%20to%20forecast%20and%20not%20a%20fundamental%20long-run%20input.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20those%20thinking%20about%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%20Young%20Thomas%20suggested%20that%20investors%20pay%20attention%20to%20how%20the%20trading%20environment%20might%20soon%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20think%3A%20'Well%2C%20okay%2C%20what%20typically%20does%20well%20during%20a%20steepening%20yield%20curve%2C%20yields%20falling%20and%20a%20falling%20dollar%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20three%20outcomes%20implied%20by%20an%20interest%20rate%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20dividend-paying%20stocks%20could%20be%20worthwhile%2C%20she%20said.%20As%20yields%20fall%2C%20Treasurys%20will%20lose%20their%20luster%2C%20sending%20investors%20in%20search%20of%20other%20income%20sources.%20Dividend%20stocks%20can%20benefit%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they're%20typically%20concentrated%20in%20utilities%20and%20staples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20dollar%20depreciation%20could%20boost%20healthcare%2C%20as%20a%20sliding%20greenback%20should%20prompt%20medical%20exports%20to%20rise%2C%20she%20said.%20Elevated%20trade%20activity%20would%20also%20benefit%20the%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurnquist%20also%20noted%20that%20investors%20might%20do%20well%20to%20buy%20the%20seasonal%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuying%20the%20September%20or%20October%20lows%20has%20been%20a%20very%20good%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOctober%2C%20things%20start%20to%20improve%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20this%20Novembe