xpected%20the%20same%20when%20my%20father%20died.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22144477fc-1649-4d30-b53d-42af41c08bd4%5C%22%3EWe%20did%20everything%20right%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EActing%20as%20their%20power%20of%20attorney%2C%20I%20managed%20my%20parents'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-plan%5C%22%3Efinancial%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20several%20years%20before%20their%20deaths%2C%20including%20placing%20most%20of%20their%20assets%20into%20irrevocable%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20death%20of%20the%20first%20spouse%2C%20the%20trusts%20specified%20the%20person's%20remaining%20assets%20were%20to%20be%20divided%20three%20ways%3A%20%E2%85%93%20to%20the%20surviving%20spouse%20and%20%E2%85%93%20to%20each%20of%20the%20two%20children.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20complete%20the%20transfer%20over%20the%20phone%20with%20the%20brokerage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiling%20my%20mother's%20final%20tax%20returns%20was%20also%20relatively%20simple%2C%20and%20I%20took%20care%20of%20her%20outstanding%20bills%20and%20cleared%20up%20her%20affairs%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%20so%20I%20expected%20the%20same%20would%20be%20true%20after%20my%20father%20died.%20However%2C%20settling%20the%20second%20spouse's%20affairs%20was%20more%20complex%2C%20even%20with%20advance%20planning.%20Everything%20from%20wills%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanking%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20tax%20returns%20became%20more%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc2cc412-a10b-42c5-be2b-ef14d990cbb5%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20many%20loose%20ends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20have%20anticipated%20the%20extra%20work%2C%20because%20I've%20been%20through%20this%20before.%20When%20my%20father-in-law%20died%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20mother-in-law%20handled%20everything.%20Since%20they%20had%20a%20family%20trust%2C%20the%20financial%20transition%20was%20seamless.%20However%2C%20when%20she%20passed%20away%20four%20years%20later%2C%20the%20work%20fell%20to%20my%20wife%20as%20executor.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20her%20parents'%20house%20had%20to%20be%20sold%2C%20and%20even%20with%20help%20from%20family%20members%20and%20spouses%2C%20it%20took%20months%20of%20work%20to%20complete%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20my%20father's%20estate%20was%20much%20simpler.%20He%20lived%20in%20an%20assisted%20living%20facility%20and%20didn't%20have%20many%20possessions.%20My%20sister%2C%20my%20wife%2C%20and%20I%20were%20able%20to%20clear%20out%20his%20room%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%20Transferring%20his%20remaining%20trust%20assets%20to%20my%20sister%20and%20me%20took%20a%20single%20call.%20The%20outstanding%20medical%20bills%20were%20paid%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWant%20to%20plan%20ahead%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20wasn't%20all.%20My%20sister%20and%20I%20couldn't%20access%20his%20bank%20account%2C%20which%20wasn't%20in%20the%20trust%2C%20without%20a%20will.%20We%20discovered%20he%20had%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-does-a-trust-fund-work-basics%5C%22%3Ea%20trust%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20no%20will%2C%20so%20my%20sister%20had%20to%20drive%20an%20hour%20to%20a%20clerk's%20office%20and%20get%20herself%20declared%20his%20next%20of%20kin%20before%20she%20could%20close%20the%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20filing%20my%20father's%20final%20tax%20return%20has%20unexpected%20layers%20of%20complexity.%20Getting%20his%20mail%20has%20always%20been%20spotty%2C%20but%20I'd%20been%20able%20to%20find%20his%20income%20documents%20online%20in%20the%20past.%20Now%20that%20he's%20deceased%2C%20I'm%20not%20able%20to%20log%20into%20his%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20tax%20preparer%20suggested%20getting%20a%20transcript%20from%20the%20IRS%2C%20so%20I've%20started%20down%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20IRS%20paperwork%20to%20get%20his%20tax%20information%2C%20which%20I%20hope%20will%20arrive%20in%20time%20to%20file%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fhow-to-file-tax-extension%5C%22%3Etax%20extension%3C%2Fa%3E%20deadline.%20And%20because%20he%20passed%20away%20in%202023%2C%20I'll%20have%20to%20do%20another%20set%20of%20tax%20returns%20(and%20another%20round%20of%20IRS%20paperwork)%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208c26ca0-0bcb-40af-9cea-7b637b5c2b03%5C%22%3EWhat%20I've%20learned%20about%20handling%20a%20second%20parent's%20estate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20hiring%20someone%20else%20to%20handle%20your%20deceased%20parent's%20affairs%2C%20there's%20no%20easy%20way%20to%20wrap%20up%20financial%20affairs%20after%20both%20your%20parents%20are%20gone.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20things%20that%20can%20make%20the%20process%20smoother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEstate%20planning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Having%20a%20will%20and%20(if%20needed)%20trust%20documents%20prepared%20by%20a%20lawyer%20will%20make%20your%20life%20easier.%20Designating%20an%20executor%20or%20trustee%20ahead%20of%20time%20can%20also%20ease%20potential%20friction%20between%20siblings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGather%20paperwork%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20your%20parent%20is%20well%20enough%20(and%20willing)%2C%20gather%20their%20financial%20paperwork%20such%20as%20tax%20records%2C%20bank%20and%20credit%20card%20information%2C%20and%20logins%20to%20online%20accounts%20while%20they're%20still%20with%20you.%20That%20will%20be%20much%20easier%20than%20tracking%20the%20information%20down%20later.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESet%20expectations%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Don't%20expect%20to%20be%20able%20to%20wrap%20things%20up%20quickly.%20You'll%20need%20to%20wait%20at%20least%20a%20few%20months%20for%20final%20bills%20and%20possibly%20longer%20to%20finalize%20taxes%2C%20sell%20property%2C%20and%20deal%20with%20all%20the%20outstanding%20financial%20issues.%20Knowing%20what%20to%20expect%20can%20make%20the%20timeline%20less%20frustrating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELosing%20a%20parent%20is%20hard.%20Getting%20clear%20about%20the%20financial%20aspects%20ahead%20of%20time%20can%20at%20least%20lighten%20your%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20September%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwrap-up-parents-finances-after-death-challenges-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725188282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e666951fee23d78817c35db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwrap-up-parents-finances-after-death-challenges-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wrapping%20up%20my%20mother's%20fi