20touches%20on%20everything%20from%20environmental%20regulations%20to%20labor%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20Rajat%20Paharia%2C%20a%20former%20Google%20product%20manager%20who%20believes%20everyone%20should%20see%20what%20Project%202025%20could%20mean%20for%20them.%20Paharia%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.25and.me%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E25%20and%20Me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20website%20that%20allows%20viewers%20to%20sort%20by%20topic%20and%20read%20for%20themselves%20what%20the%20playbook%20has%20to%20say%20on%20issues%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elike%20civil%20rights%2C%20drug%20prices%2C%20and%20veterans%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmericans%20have%20such%20varied%20interests%20and%20are%20affected%20by%20such%20varied%20things%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20any%20one%20individual%20to%20be%20able%20to%20find%20all%20the%20information%20that's%20relative%20to%20them%20and%20how%20this%20might%20impact%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Paharia%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20was%20clearly%20kind%20of%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%20here%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20and%20potentially%2C%20I%20could%20make%20something%20to%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Paharia%20about%20three%20days%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Google%20Gemini%20and%20GitHub%20Copilot%2C%20to%20create%20the%20website.%20The%20AI%20tools%20helped%20him%20identify%20excerpts%20in%20the%20playbook%20that%20touched%20on%20various%20topics%20and%20then%20listed%20each%20reference%20with%20citations%20to%20its%20source%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20know%20what%20Project%202025%20says%20about%20food%20stamps%3F%20Check%20pages%20298-303.%20Reproductive%20rights%3F%20References%20start%20around%20page%20450.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20and%20over%20again%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20many%20people%20in%20this%20country%20have%20voted%20against%20their%20own%20self-interest%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20I%20believe%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0potentially%20naively%20or%20foolishly%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20because%20they%20don't%20know%20that's%20what%20they're%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Paharia%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20voting%20on%20a%20certain%20set%20of%20issues%20that%20they%20understand%20and%20hear%20about%20and%20know%20about%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20understand%20the%20other%20things%20that%20their%20elected%20representatives%20are%20pushing%20or%20standing%20behind%20that%20will%20negatively%20affect%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20campaign%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Project%202025%20after%20a%20swath%20of%20bad%20press%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemocrats-project-2025-harris-trump-dlcc-conservatives-states-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattacks%20by%20Democrats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20former%20president%20claimed%20last%20month%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20idea%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20behind%20the%20playbook.%20However%2C%20numerous%20reports%20indicate%20that%20over%20140%20former%20Trump%20administration%20members%20had%20contributed%20to%20Project%202025%2C%20and%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation%20has%20historically%20had%20close%20ties%20to%20the%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-2025-search-tool-ai-google-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725187681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d39647289b805d1db35769%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-2025-search-tool-ai-google-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20most%20important%20parts%20of%20Project%202025%20are%20buried%20in%20its%20900-page%20playbook.%20This%20ex-Google%20project%20manager%20just%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20sift%20through.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A447%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-2025-search-tool-ai-google-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAdding%20Salt%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Veep's%20Fresh%20Fire%20At%20Kapil%20Sibal%20Over%20Kolkata%20Horror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20had%20shamed%20humanity%20and%20%26quot%3Bsome%20stray%20voices%26quot%3B%20are%20aggravating%20the%20pain%2C%20Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20said%20today%2C%20launching%20a%20fresh%20attack%20on%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Vice-President%20said%20at%20a%20public%20event%20that%20someone%20holding%20a%20position%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bar%20and%20also%20a%20member%20of%20Parliament%20had%20said%20the%20Kolkata%20incident%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymptomatic%20malaise%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20that%20such%20incidents%20are%20commonplace.%20The%20remark%20was%20aimed%20at%20Mr%20Sibal%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20president%20who%20is%20also%20representing%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20in%20the%20sensitive%20rape-murder%20case.%20Mr%20Sibal%20purportedly%20used%20the%20expression%20in%20a%20resolution%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%2C%20of%20which%20he%20is%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20event%20at%20AIIMS%20Rishikesh%20today%2C%20the%20Vice-President%20said%20incidents%20like%20the%20one%20in%20Kolkata%20put%20the%20entire%20civilisation%20to%20shame.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20humanity%20has%20been%20shamed%2C%20there%20are%20some%20stray%20voices%2C%20voices%20that%20cause%20concern.%20They%20only%20aggravate%20our%20excruciating%20pain.%20To%20put%20it%20mildly%20they%20are%20adding%20salt%20to%20our%20injured%20conscience.%20What%20do%20they%20say%2C%20'it%20is%20a%20symptomatic%20malaise%2C%20a%20frequent%20incident'.%20When%20it%20comes%20from%20someone%20who%20is%20the%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20a%20senior%20advocate%2C%20then%20the%20culpability%20is%20of%20extreme%20degree%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20alibi%20for%20such%20kind%20of%20demonising%20thoughts.%20I%20call%20upon%20such%20misguided%20souls%20to%20revisit%20their%20thoughts%20and%20publicly%20tender%20apology.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20occasion%20where%20you%20should%20be%20looking%20through%20political%20prism.%20This%20political%20prism%20is%20a%20dangerous%20one%2C%20it%20kills%20your%20objectivity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Vice-President%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice-President%20underlined%20the%20need%20for%20safety%20of%20doctors%20at%20the%20workplace.%20%26quot%3BA%20doctor%20can%20help%20only%20to%20a%20limit.%20A%20doctor%20cannot%20convert%20himself%20to%20god.%20He%20is%20next%20to%20God%2C%20so%20when%20somebody%20dies%2C%20out%20of%20emotive%20feelings%20and%20uncontrolled%20feelings%2C%20doctors%20are%20not%20given%20the%20treatment%20they%20deserve...%20.security%20of%20the%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20compounders%2C%20health%20warriors%20must%20be%20impregnably%20protected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice-President%20also%20criticised%20the%20%26quot%3Bselective%20silence%26quot%3B%20of%20NGOs.%20%26quot%3BCertain%20NGOs%20on%20road%20for%20drop%20of%20an%20incident%2C%20drop%20of%20a%20hat%20are%20in%20Silence%20mode.%20We%20have%20to%20question%20them.%20Their%20silence%20is%20much%20worse%20than%20the%20culpable%20act%20of%20perpetrators%20of%20this%20heinous%20crime%20on%20August%209%202024.%20Those%20who%20seek%20to%20play%20politics%20and%20earn%20brownie%20points%2C%20are%20not%20responding%20to%20the%20call%20of%20their%20conscience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20an%20occasion%20to%20earn%20Brownie%20points%2C%20score%20political%20mileage.%20This%20is%20non%20partisan.%20It%20requires%20bi-partisan%20concerted%20efforts.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20for%20convergence%20of%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20democracy%2C%20to%20come%20together%20on%20one%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20had%20expressed%20her%20anguish%20at%20the%20crimes%20against%20women.%20Saying%20that%20%26quot%3Benough%20is%20enough%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20had%20said%20it%20is%20time%20for%20India%20to%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bperversion%26quot%3B%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20counter%20the%20mindset%20that%20sees%20women%20as%20%26quot%3Bless%20powerful%2C%20less%20capable%2C%20less%20intelligent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725187440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F8d0karmg_veep-sibal_625x300_01_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-kapil-sibal-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-adding-salt-to-veeps-fresh-fire-at-kapil-sibal-over-kolkata-horror-6466019%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20had%20shamed%20humanity%20and%20%26quot%3Bsome%20stray%20voices%26quot%3B%20are%20aggravating%20the%20pain%2C%20Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20said%20today%2C%20launching%20a%20fresh%20attack%20on%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-kapil-sibal-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-adding-salt-to-veeps-fresh-fire-at-kapil-sibal-over-kolkata-horror-6466019%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20why%20Gen%20Z%20loses%20more%20money%20to%20online%20scams%20than%20boomers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gen%20Z%2