0payment%20in%20the%20legal%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-models-microsoft-openai-meta-google-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-powered%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20expected%20to%20become%20widely%20adopted%20in%20the%20legal%20field%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20industry%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20use%20of%20the%20rapidly%20advancing%20technology%20won't%20kill%20off%20the%20billable%20hour%20payment%20model%2C%20but%20rather%20reinvent%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20attorneys%20said%20that%20as%20AI%20tools%20are%20used%20at%20firms%20to%20automate%20routine%20and%20time-consuming%20grunt%20work%20tasks%20like%20document%20review%20and%20due%20diligence%2C%20the%20number%20of%20billable%20hours%20to%20a%20client%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20reduced%2C%20and%20the%20value%20of%20a%20lawyer's%20individual%20hour%20is%20likely%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20value%20that%20lawyers%20provide%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20that's%20strategic%20advice%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20it's%20the%20actual%20drafting%20of%20arguments%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20it's%20the%20arguing%20in%20court%20to%20jurors%20or%20to%20judges%20in%20courtrooms%2C%20or%20to%20the%20making%20of%20deals%20and%20negotiating%20terms%20%E2%80%94%20all%20those%20sorts%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20an%20increasing%20premium%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michel%20Paradis%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20global%20firm%20Curtis%2C%20Mallet-Prevost%2C%20Colt%20%26amp%3B%20Mosle%20LLP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParadis%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20AI-related%20legal%20work%20and%20also%20teaches%20national%20security%20and%20constitutional%20law%20at%20Columbia%20Law%20School%2C%20said%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20there%20will%20ever%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20disappearance%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolar-sonnedix-legal-eliminated-billable-hour-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillable%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20law%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20think%20you're%20likely%20to%20see%20is%20a%20slow%20disappearance%20of%20the%20filler%20billable%20hours%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20slew%20of%20law%20firms%20depend%20on%2C%20Paradis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20way%20that%20the%20introduction%20of%20word%20processors%20dramatically%20shifted%20the%20way%20law%20firms%20operated%20in%20the%20late%2020th%20century%2C%20Paradis%20said%20he%20foresees%20the%20same%20thing%20happening%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20going%20to%20have%20a%20similar%20effect%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20information%20technology%20in%20the%20legal%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paradis%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20that%20is%20a%20consistent%20gobbling%20up%20of%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20legal%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElisa%20Botero%2C%20another%20partner%20at%20the%20New%20York-headquartered%20firm%2C%20agreed%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20billable%20hour%20model%20will%20remain%20a%20%26quot%3Bkey%20metric%26quot%3B%20for%20at%20least%20the%20foreseeable%20future%20even%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-law-firms-using-ai-fast-track-ma-deals-work-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20law%20firms%20move%20to%20utilize%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20boost%20the%20efficiency%20of%20their%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20type%20of%20work%20will%20be%20billed%20out%20will%20shift%20and%20is%20already%20shifting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Botero%2C%20explaining%20that%20more%20traditional%2C%20associate-type%20work%20or%20junior-level%20work%20will%20be%20most%20impacted%20by%20the%20use%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20still%20see%20billable%20hours%2C%20but%20you'll%20see%20a%20reduction%20of%20those%20billable%20hours%20for%20that%20type%20of%20routine%20legal