ddhav%20Thackeray%20today%20claimed%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20apology%20on%20the%20statue%20collapse%20smacked%20of%20arrogance%20and%20added%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20had%20rejected%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20during%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi's%20%26quot%3Bjode%20maro%26quot%3B%20protest%20--%20meaning%20hit%20with%20footwear%20--%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Maratha%20ruler's%20statue%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20drew%20a%20parallel%20between%20the%20statue's%20collapse%20and%20water%20dripping%20into%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20new%20Parliament%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20notice%20the%20arrogance%20in%20the%20(Prime%20Minister's)%20apology%3F%20It%20smacked%20of%20arrogance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20what%20was%20the%20PM%20apologising%3F%20For%20the%20statue%20he%20inaugurated%20eight%20months%20ago%3F%20For%20the%20corruption%20involved%3F%20The%20MVA%20cadre%20must%20work%20together%20to%20defeat%20the%20forces%20that%20have%20insulted%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20The%20collapse%20of%20the%20statue%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20soul%20of%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20apologised%20to%20the%20followers%20of%20Shivaji%20for%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20statue%2C%20which%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20massive%20political%20row%20months%20before%20Maharashtra%20votes%20in%20Assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20is%20not%20just%20a%20name%20or%20a%20king.%20For%20us%2C%20he%20is%20our%20deity.%20Today%2C%20I%20bow%20my%20head%20at%20his%20feet%20and%20apologise%20to%20my%20deity.%20I%20also%20apologise%20to%20the%20people%20hurt%20by%20the%20collapse%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20have%20slammed%20the%20Opposition's%20protest%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20politicising%20the%20issue%20even%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20charge%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20doing%20politics%2C%20but%20we%20are%20fighting%20for%20the%20state's%20glory.%20We%20have%20come%20to%20the%20Gateway%20of%20India%20to%20say%20'get%20out'%20to%20the%20Mahayuti%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Maharashtra%20--%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Nana%20Patole%20took%20part%20in%20the%20protest%20march%20that%20started%20at%20Hutatma%20Chowk%20and%20reached%20Gateway%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20collapse%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj's%20statue%20in%20Sindhudurg%20is%20an%20example%20of%20corruption.%20It%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20all%20Shiv%20premis%20(followers%20of%20Shivaji).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patole%2C%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%2C%20said%20the%20Opposition%20had%20sought%20Shivaji's%20forgiveness%20for%20allowing%20such%20a%20%26quot%3BShiv%20drohi%26quot%3B%20government%20to%20come%20to%20power.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20a%20pledge%20to%20never%20let%20it%20happen%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%20and%20said%20Shivaji%20cannot%20be%20a%20political%20issue.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20identity%20and%20faith%20for%20us.%20The%20incident%20that%20happened%20was%20unfortunate.%20The%20opposition%20is%20doing%20politics%20on%20this.%20Two%20JCBs%20were%20brought%20to%20break%20the%20statue%20of%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20that%20statue%20was%20uprooted%2C%20those%20who%20did%20this%20should%20be%20beaten.%20Instead%20of%20doing%20this%2C%20they%20(MVA)%20are%20protesting%20here%2C%20but%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20are%20wise%2C%20they%20are%20watching.%20In%20the%20coming%20elections%2C%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20will%20beat%20them%20with%20shoes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20too%2C%20has%20said%20the%20Opposition%20is%20politicising%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BFor%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20are%20insulting%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20never%20spoke%20a%20word%20about%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20from%20Red%20Fort%2C%20will%20the%20Congress%20apologise%3F%20PM%20Modi%20has%20apologised%2C%20but%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20leaders%20are%20politicising%20the%20issue%20because%20the%20polls%20are%20approaching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shivaji%20statue%20at%20Sindhudurg%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20just%208%20months%20back.%20The%20project%20was%20handled%20by%20the%20Navy%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20state%20government.%20Police%20have%20arrested%20the%20structural%20consultant%20for%20the%20project%20and%20its%20contractor.%20They%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20culpable%20homicide%20and%20act%20endangering%20life%20and%20safety%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725183000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F0on9h6qg_uddhav-thackeray_625x300_01_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivaji-statue-collapse-jode-maro-protest-pms-shivaji-statue-collapse-apology-smacked-of-arrogance-uddhav-thackeray-6465585%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tearing%20into%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%2035-foot%20statue%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%2C%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20today%20claimed%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20apology%20on%20the%20statue%20collapse%20smacked%20of%20arrogance%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22