0title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fr8pmhc7_noorani_625x300_01_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20A.G.%20Noorani%20came%20to%20Kochi%2C%20where%20I%20and%20a%20few%20colleagues%20in%20my%20litigation%20firm%20had%20the%20privilege%20to%20invite%20him%20for%20dinner.%20His%20penchant%20for%20food%20was%20known%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20that%20we%20treated%20him%20well.%20He%20spoke%20at%20length%20with%20the%20young%20lawyers%20even%20after%20his%20long%20lecture%20during%20a%20seminar%20in%20the%20city.%20He%20was%20curious%20to%20know%20how%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20practising%20lawyers%20perceived%20the%20juridical%20and%20political%20developments%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20my%20only%20personal%20account%20with%20the%20constitutional%20legend.%20Yet%2C%20his%20columns%20and%20books%20had%20a%20formidable%20influence%20on%20me%2C%20like%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20counsel%2C%20Noorani%20was%20engaged%20in%201962%20to%20defend%20Sheik%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20was%20treated%20unfairly%20and%20put%20in%20prison%20by%20the%20then%20Congress%20Government.%20Not%20only%20did%20he%20do%20his%20work%20as%20the%20defence%20counsel%2C%20but%20he%20went%20much%20beyond%20the%20brief%2C%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%20That%20led%20to%20seminal%20works%20which%20came%20out%20decades%20later%2C%20like%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKashmir%20Dispute%3A%201947-2012%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eand%C2%A0%3Ci%3EArticle%20370%3A%20A%20Constitutional%20History%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fi%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoorani%20Couldn't%20Be%20Limited%20By%20Narrowness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoorani's%20success%20transcended%20the%20traditional%20limits%20of%20his%20profession.%20Neither%20his%20critical%20intellect%20nor%20his%20razor-sharp%20analytical%20skills%20could%20be%20limited%20by%20the%20narrowness%20of%20a%20case%20brief.%20He%20became%20a%20true%20public%20intellectual%20with%20a%20high%20level%20of%20ethical%20and%20intellectual%20integrity.%20His%20works%2C%20ranging%20from%3Ci%3E%C2%A0Constitutional%20Questions%20in%20India%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eto%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Babri%20Masjid%20Question%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20reveal%20not%20merely%20his%20trajectory%20as%20a%20lawyer-writer%2C%20but%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20country's%20democracy%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoorani's%20life%20conveys%20a%20unique%20message.%20In%20the%20legal%20profession%2C%20diplomacy%20matters%2C%20while%20as%20a%20public%20intellectual%2C%20honesty%20and%20integrity%20alone%20count.%20There%20could%20be%20occasions%20where%20one%20will%20have%20to%20choose%20one%20of%20the%20either.%20In%20such%20times%2C%20Noorani%20always%20preferred%20the%20more%20difficult%20terrain%20of%20utmost%20uprightness.%20And%20this%20made%20him%20a%20jurist%20unparalleled.%20Very%20rarely%20a%20lawyer%20in%20India%20has%20integrated%20his%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20acumen%20so%20intensely%20with%20the%20country's%20political%20history.%20As%20Malayalam%20writer%20Sukumar%20Azhikode%20said%20about%20Gandhiji%2C%20Noorani%2C%20too%2C%20succeeded%20over%20the%20profession%2C%20not%20merely%20in%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Noorani%20Said%20About%20Sedition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20essayist%2C%20Noorani%20was%20exceptionally%20analytical.%20Critical%20intellect%20was%20the%20hallmark%20of%20his%20legal%20acumen%20that%20had%20its%20roots%20deep%20in%20the%20other%20branches%20of%20knowledge%2C%20including%20literature.%20He%20never%20adopted%20a%20textual%20or%20superficial%20view%20of%20any%20topic.%20His%20analysis%20of%20the%20judgment%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKedar%20Nath%20Singh%20vs.%20State%20of%20Bihar%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E(1962)%20by%20the%20Constitution%20Bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20validated%20the%20sedition%20law%20is%20emblematic%20of%20his%20capacity%20to%20scan%20the%20subject.%20Many%20believe%20that%20the%20validation%20of%20the%20illiberal%20provision%20was%20wrong%20and%20outdated.%20Countries%20including%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20from%20which%20the%20law%20originated%2C%20have%20done%20away%20with%20it.%20There%20is%20a%20line%20of%20thinking%20on%20and%20off%20the%20Bench%20that%20the%20judgment%20requires%20reconsideration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Noorani%20wrote%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20he%20called%20it%20not%20merely%20wrong%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cdisastrous%E2%80%9D.%20He%20praised%20K.M.%20Munshi's%20efforts%20during%20the%20Constitutional%20Assembly%20debates%20that%20led%20to%20the%20deletion%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98sedition'%20from%20the%20country's%20Constitution.%20Noorani%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20lasting%20disgrace%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20brought%20%5Bthe%20provision%20on%20sedition%5D%20back%20by%20the%20back%20door%2014%20years%20later%2C%20ignoring%20totally%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%20and%20the%20enormous%20labour%20preceding%20it%E2%80%9D.%20Thus%2C%20Noorani%20criticised%20not%20only%20the%20judgment%20in%20%3Cem%3EKedar%20Nath%20Singh%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20also%20the%20callousness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20judges%20in%20examining%20the%20issue.%20In%20another%20essay%2C%20he%20elaborated%20on%20sedition%20cases%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20A%20sense%20of%20history%20enables%20us%20to%20understand%20the%20evolution%20of%20law%20better%2C%20to%20spot%20the%20aberrations%20in%20the%20process%20and%20to%20correct%20the%20historical%20errors.%20Indian%20courts%2C%20too%2C%20will%20miss%20Noorani%20who%20formed%20an%20authoritative%20resource%20on%20such%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFearlessness%20Is%20A%20Virtue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoorani's%20respectability%20went%20beyond%20the%20boundaries%20of%20law.%20He%20continued%20to%20astonish%20quixotic%20and%20hollow%20legal%20technocrats%20on%20the%20Bench%20and%20in%20the%20Bar.%20He%20excelled%20not%20only%20in%20the%20text%20of%20the%20Constitution%20but%20also%20in%20his%20struggle%20to%20maintain%20its%20eternal%20values.%20There%20is%20no%20democracy%20without%20ideas%20like%20secularism%2C%20federalism%2C%20and%20human%20dignity%2C%20and%20Noorani%20insisted%20on%20their%20invocation%20in%20the%20process%20of%20governance.%20The%20wide%20range%20of%20titles%20by%20Noorani%20covered%20major%20issues%20like%20the%20growing%20threat%20of%20communalism%2C%20the%20system%20of%20governance%2C%20abuse%20of%20power%20by%20public%20functionaries%20like%20governors%20and%20ministers.%20His%20well-researched%20works%20vary%20from%20Bhagat%20Singh's%20trial%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFearlessness%20is%20a%20captivating%20quality%20that%20the%20Bombay%20Bar%20has%20taught%20the%20nation.%20Constitutional%20scholar%20H.M.%20Seervai%20said%20that%20courage%20is%20the%20greatest%20virtue%20for%20a%20lawyer%2C%20for%20without%20courage%2C%20there%20is%20no%20truth.%20Noorani%20embodied%20this%20forensic%20reality%2C%20both%20as%20a%20lawyer%20and%20as%20a%20writer.%20The%20fearlessness%20of%20this%20man%20is%20also%20antithetical%20to%20practical%20diplomacy.%20As%20an%20intellectual%2C%20he%20did%20not%20believe%20in%20flattery.%20Those%20in%20power%2C%20whether%20political%20or%20judicial%2C%20had%20to%20confront%20the%20creativity%20of%20his%20freedom%20and%20the%20objectivity%20of%20his%20analysis.%20His%20writing%2C%20which%20began%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20stretched%20over%20a%20period%20of%20six%20decades.%20His%20encyclopaedic%20knowledge%20about%20the%20minute%20personal%2C%20political%20and%20historical%20details%20of%20the%20major%20events%20in%20the%20country's%20history%20would%20provide%20for%20a%20unique%20sense%20of%20authenticity%20to%20whatever%20he%20writes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeyond%20Temporal%20Gains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20these%20lines%20get%20published%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20many%20will%20have%20come%20on%20record%20recalling%20the%20unique%20life%20of%20A.G.%20Noorani.%20The%20love%20and%20admiration%20that%20the%20country%20showered%20on%20him%20would%20surpass%20that%20which%20many%20of%20the%20stalwarts%20in%20the%20Indian%20Bar%20who%20engaged%20exclusively%20in%20the%20court%20battles%20could%20have%20enjoyed.%20Why%20is%20that%20so%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20is%20also%20another%20plain%20truth.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20money%20or%20professional%20success%20that%20ultimately%20matters.%20The%20eternal%20value%20of%20the%20human%20intellect%2C%20philosophy%20and%20reflection%20is%20an%20encouragement%20to%20all%20those%20who%20think%20beyond%20temporal%20gains.%20Noorani%20lived%20a%20life%20that%20was%20larger%20than%20life%20and%20stronger%20than%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Kaleeswaram%20Raj%20is%20a%20lawyer%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725182700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fci9u0ihg_noorani_625x300_01_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-g-noorani-larger-than-life-stronger-than-death-6465256%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Malayalam%20writer%20Sukumar%20Azhikode%20said%20about%20Gandhiji%2C%20Noorani%2C%20too%2C%20succeeded%20over%20the%20legal%20profession%2C%20not%20merely%20in%20the%20profession.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-g-noorani-larger-than-life-stronger-than-death-6465256%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EU%20airports%20see%20100ml%20liquid%20rule%20reintroduced%22%2C%22content%