e%20occasion%20of%20Navy%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20(SP)%20supremo%20Pawar%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Thackeray%2C%20Congress%20state%20unit%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20the%20party's%20Mumbai%20head%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20began%20the%20protest%20march%20by%20laying%20wreaths%20at%20Hutatma%20Chowk%2C%20a%20memorial%20to%20those%20martyred%20in%20the%20'Samyukta%20Maharashtra'%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20at%20Gateway%20of%20India%2C%20where%20the%20protest%20march%20culminated%2C%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20you%20notice%20the%20arrogance%20in%20the%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's)%20apology%3F%20It%20smacked%20of%20arrogance.%20One%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20was%20smiling.%26quot%3B%20Asserting%20that%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20will%20never%20forgive%20the%20insult%20to%20the%20legendary%20warrior%20king%2C%20Thackeray%20cited%20the%20statue%20collapse%2C%20leakages%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20the%20new%20Parliament%20complex%20to%20mock%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bguarantees%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20what%20was%20the%20PM%20apologising%3F%20For%20the%20statue%20he%20inaugurated%20eight%20months%20ago%3F%20For%20the%20corruption%20involved%3F%20The%20MVA%20cadre%20must%20work%20together%20to%20defeat%20the%20forces%20that%20have%20insulted%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20The%20collapse%20of%20the%20statue%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20soul%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%20in%20Palghar%20on%20Friday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20is%20not%20just%20a%20name%20or%20a%20king%20but%20a%20deity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20bow%20my%20head%20at%20his%20feet%20and%20apologise%20to%20my%20deity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20protest%20march%2C%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20collapse%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj's%20statue%20in%20Sindhudurg%20is%20an%20example%20of%20corruption.%20It%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20all%20Shiv%20premis%20(followers%20of%20the%20warrior%20king).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolhapur%20Congress%20MP%20Shahu%20Chhatrapati%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20emperor%2C%20said%20the%20latter's%20dignity%20must%20be%20maintained%20at%20all%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20march%2C%20which%20began%20sometime%20after%2011am%2C%20included%20NCP%20(SP)%20Baramati%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20MLA%20Anil%20Deshmukh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bust%20of%20the%20legendary%20warrior%20king%20was%20placed%20at%20Hutatma%20Chowk%2C%20while%20those%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20protest%20march%20carried%20placards%20denouncing%20the%20statue%20collapse%20and%20shouted%20slogans%20against%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20(SP)%20chief%20Pawar%20walked%20some%20distance%20as%20part%20of%20the%20protest%20march%20before%20getting%20into%20his%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725178800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fhcqeji4g_uddhav_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcollapse-of-shivaji-statue-insult-to-maharashtra-uddhav-thackeray-6464965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leaders%20of%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20on%20Sunday%20held%20a%20march%20from%20the%20iconic%20Hutatma%20Chowk%20to%20Gateway%20of%20India%20in%20south%20Mumbai%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sindhudurg%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcollapse-of-shivaji-statue-insult-to-maharashtra-uddhav-thackeray-6464965%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20Is%20No%20'Power%20Centre'%26quot%3B%3A%20Actor%20Mammootty%20Amid%20Mollywood%20%23MeToo%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20storm%20in%20Mollywood%20surrounding%20sexual%20assault%20allegations%20against%20some%20top%20actors%20and%20directors%2C%20legendary%20actor%20Mammooty%20has%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20power%20centre%26quot%3B%20in%20Malayalam%20cinema%20and%20appealed%20to%20police%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20honestly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Mohanlal%2C%20another%20top%20actor%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%2C%20said%20that%20neither%20was%20he%20a%20part%20of%20any%20power%20group%20in%20Mollywood%2C%20nor%20was%20he%20aware%20of%20any%20such%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%2072-year-old%20Mammootty%20said%20cinema%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20society%20and%20the%20good%20and%20bad%20in%20the%20society%20are%20also%20present%20in%20the%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20formed%20to%20suggest%20solutions%20and%20recommend%20measures%20after%20something%20that%20should%20never%20have%20happened.%20Welcoming%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20panel%2C%20Mammooty%20said%20police%20investigation%20is%20proceeding%20swiftly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20full%20version%20of%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20committee%20report%20is%20before%20the%20court.%20Let%20the%20police%20investigate%20honestly.%20Let%20the%20court%20decide%20the%20punishments.%20There%20is%20no%20'powerhouse'%20in%20cinema%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20actor%20said%20the%20norm%20is%20that%20the%20actors'%20organisation%20responds%20to%20such%20issues%20first.%20He%20said%20he%20waited%20this%20long%20for%20this%20very%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment%20against%20some%20top%20actors%20and%20filmmakers.%20Actors%20Jayasurya%20Sidhique%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20Maniyanpilla%20Raju%2C%20Idavela%20Babu%20and%20director%20Ranjith%20are%20among%20the%20prominent%20film%20personalities%20who%20now%20face%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20assault.%20Several%20actors%2C%20including%20Minu%20Muneer%20and%20Sonia%20Malhaar%2C%20have%20brought%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flood%20of%20allegations%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20public%20release%20of%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20last%20week.%20The%20235-page%20report%2C%20published%20after%20redacting%20names%20of%20witnesses%20and%20the%20accused%2C%20notes%20that%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20is%20controlled%20by%2010-15%20male%20producers%2C%20directors%2C%20and%20actors.%20The%20three-member%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%202017%20and%20submitted%20its%20report%20in%202019.%20The%20report%20was%20not%20made%20public%20so%20far%20due%20to%20legal%20challenges%20to%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20uproar%20has%20led%20to%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20top%20panel%20of%20Association%20of%20Malayalam%20Movie%20Artists%20or%20AMMA.%20The%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20Mohanlal%20as%20president%2C%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20moral%20responsibility%20%26quot%3Bin%20light%20of%20allegations%20made%20by%20some%20actors%20against%20some%20of%20the%20committee%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20is%20now%20probing%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20evening%2C%20Mohanlal%20said%20the%20film%20industry%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20questions%20raised%2C%20but%20the%20actors'%20association%20is%20targeted%20and%20blamed%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20part%20of%20any%20power%20group%20in%20Malayalam%20cinema%20and%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20any%20such%20group.%20I%20have%20heard%20about%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20allegations%20against%20AMMA%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAMMA%20is%20not%20an%20outfit%20with%20trade%20union%20nature.%20It%20was%20launched%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20its%20members....The%20entire%20film%20industry%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20questions%20regarding%20the%20Hema%20panel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20associations%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20AMMA%20is%20blamed%20for%20everything.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20right%20to%20crucify%20an%20outfit%20alone%20for%20all%20these%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohanlal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725178740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2F17ujb59_mammootty-instagram_625x300_18_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-is-no-power-centre-actor-mammootty-amid-mollywood-metoo-row-6465035%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20storm%20in%20Mollywood%20surrounding%20sexual%20assault%20allegations%20against%20some%20top%20actors%20and%20directors%2C%20legendary%20actor%20Mammooty%20has%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20power%20centre%26quot%3B%20in%20Malayalam%20cinema%20and%20appealed%20to%20police%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20honestly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-is-no-power-centre-actor-mammootty-amid-mollywood-metoo-row-6465035%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asked%20About%20Breaking%20Tendulkar's%20Record%2C%20Joe%20Root's%20Answer%20Wins%20Internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEngland%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Root%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.co