%20smart.%20During%20an%20interaction%20on%20the%C2%A0%C2%A0YouTube%20podcast%20show%20'Unplugged'%2C%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20has%20officiated%20in%20over%2050%20international%20matches%2C%20said%20that%20people%20have%20a%20somewhat%20wrong%20impression%20of%20Rohit%20as%20he%20is%20a%20very%20smart%20cricketer%20and%20added%20that%20fans%20and%20experts%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20get%20fooled%26quot%3B%20in%20doubting%20his%20game%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERohit%20aapko%20lagta%20casual%20hai%20par%20bahot%20smart%20player%20hai.%20Iss%20chakkar%20mein%20na%20padna%20aap.%20He%20is%20very%20smart.%20Cricketing%20IQ%20bahut%20achha%20hai%20uska%2C%20means%20game%20ki%20samajh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Rohit%20may%20seem%20casual%2C%20but%20he's%20a%20very%20smart%20player%2C%20don't%20get%20fooled%20thinking%20otherwise%3B%20his%20game%20sense%20is%20very%20good)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EUski%20Batting%20se%20idea%20nahi%20aata%20aapko.%20Jab%20wo%20batting%20karta%20hai%20to%20lagta%20hai%20120%20(kmph)%20pe%20bowling%20ho%20rahi%20hai.%20Jab%20dusra%20batting%20karta%20hai%20to%20lagta%20hai%20160%20pe%20bowling%20ho%20rahi%20hai....Wo%20bahut%20saari%20appealon%20mein%20aa%20jata%20hai%20aur%20kehta%20hai%20'abey%20rehne%20de'.%20Woh%20lagta%20casual%20hai%20par%20casual%20bilkul%20nahi%20hai%20woh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(you%20can't%20guess%20his%20sharp%20mind%20from%20his%20batting.%20When%20he's%20batting%2C%20it%20seems%20someone%20is%20bowling%20at%20120%20kmph%2C%20but%20when%20someone%20else%20is%20batting%2C%20the%20speed%20seems%20like%20160%20kmph.%20He%20gets%20involved%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20appeals%20and%20then%20says%20'let%20it%20be.'%20He%20may%20seem%20casual%2C%20but%20he's%20not%20casual%20at%20all).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20umpiring%20is%20quite%20easy%20against%20a%20player%20like%20Rohit%20as%20he%20does%20not%20play%20'confusingly'%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20his%20dismissals%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20'straightforward'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERohit%20jaise%20player%20ke%20liye%20umpiring%20karna%20bada%20easy%20hai.%20Ya%20to%20out%20hota%20hai%20ya%20to%20not%20out%20hota%20hai.%20Seedha%20seedha%20kaam%20hai%20uska.%20Guchur%20guchur%20khelta%20hi%20nahi%20hai%20wo.%20Woh%20out%20hai%20ya%20not%20out%20hai.%20Aise%20player%20ko%20umpiring%20karna%20bahot%20easy%20hai.%20Usko%20dekhna%20aap%2C%20ya%20to%20woh%20saaf%20out%20hoga%20ya%20saaf%20not%20out%20hoga%20%3C%2Fem%3E(umpiring%20for%20a%20player%20like%20Rohit%20is%20very%20easy%3B%20he's%20either%20out%20or%20not%20out%2C%20it's%20straightforward%20with%20him.%20He%20doesn't%20play%20confusingly)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725173220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F26s5jvi4_rohit-sharma_625x300_22_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdont-get-fooled-umpire-gives-sensational-smart-verdict-on-rohit-sharma-6464519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20a%20reputation%20of%20being%20a%20calm%20and%20composed%20person%20with%20stories%20of%20his%20forgetfulness%20being%20quite%20popular.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdont-get-fooled-umpire-gives-sensational-smart-verdict-on-rohit-sharma-6464519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20getting%20kicked%20off%20because%20...%E2%80%99%3A%20Man%20kicked%20off%20Delta%20Airlines%20flight%20for%20wearing%20offensive%20Trump%20shirt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725173195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112964370%2Cimgsize-752010.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fim-getting-kicked-off-because-man-kicked-of