e%20at%20home%20with%20his%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20along%20with%20a%20parent%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20it%2C%20Suman%20Khanna%2C%20counselling%20psychologist%20and%20founder%2C%20Mind%20Unwind%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20says%20that%20this%20is%20when%20they%20start%20understanding%20the%20world%20and%20environment%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20life%2C%20especially%20the%20first%20six%20months%2C%20a%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20ask%20for%20something.%20The%20presence%20of%20a%20parent%20to%20comfort%20them%20makes%20the%20child%20feel%20safe%20and%20creates%20a%20secure%20attachment%20style.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20child%20starts%20trusting%20his%20or%20her%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%2C%20Harpreet%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CParenting%20is%20not%20about%20the%20child%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20parent.%20Having%20a%20child%20gives%20us%20a%20window%20of%20opportunity%20to%20genuinely%20reflect%20and%20change%20ourselves.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Harpreet%20started%20enjoying%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349527%2Fnew-mothers-online-support-groups-postpartum-breastfeeding-formula-sleep-training-parenting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehands-on%20father%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20had%20a%20blast%20with%20his%20daughter.%20He%20would%20take%20her%20to%20the%20park%2C%20the%20swimming%20pool%20and%20just%20enjoyed%20being%20a%20parent.%20This%20allowed%20him%20to%20notice%20how%20other%20children%20interacted%20with%20their%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20an%20example%20of%20a%20swimming%20class.%20Despite%20some%20children%E2%80%99s%20fear%2C%20the%20instructor%20simply%20throws%20the%20child%20in%20the%20water.%20But%20h