r%20the%20subject.%20To%20further%20their%20interest%2C%20they%20joined%20Omotec%20and%20did%20a%20course%20in%20Python%2C%20a%20programming%20language.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20done%20various%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334179%2Fteenage-changemakers-of-india-children-founders-of-startups-ngos-inspiring%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourses%20in%20robotics%2C%20coding%2C%20electronics%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20STEM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rahi%20and%20Hriday%20with%20their%20innovation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571-500x334.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571-768x513.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362424%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%20with%20their%20innovation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20basic%20Lego%20robots%20to%20creating%20industrial%20products.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20learning%20about%20electronics%20and%20coding%2C%20and%20participating%20in%20various%20national%20competitions%20where%20we%20can%20use%20our%20knowledge%20practically%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IRIS%20(Initiative%20for%20Research%20and%20Innovation%20in%20STEM)%20National%20Fair%20was%20the%20proverbial%20game%20changer%20for%20these%20young%20innovators.%20After%20enrolling%20for%20the%20same%20in%202022%2C%20they%20were%20challenged%20to%20create%20a%20working%20prototype%20for%20a%20topic%20they%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20no%20limits%20to%20what%20we%20could%20create.%20We%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20be%20genuinely%20useful%20to%20our%20families.%20Since%20both%20of%20our%20grandmothers%20had%20mobility%20issues%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20developing%20a%20solution%20for%20elders%20like%20them%20to%20help%20prevent%20falls.%20If%20we%20had%20known%20about%20her%20condition%20earlier%2C%20we%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20address%20it%20more%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Hriday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20ignited%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20device%20that%20could%20offer%20early%20detection%20of%20mobility%20issues%2C%20potentially%20preventing%20severe%20health%20complications%20down%20the%20line.%20Intense%20brainstorming%20sessions%20followed%2C%20where%20wheelchairs%2C%20walking%20sticks%20and%20more%20were%20discussed.%20%E2%80%9CShould%20it%20be%20a%20foldable%20walking%20stick%2C%20a%20single%20cane%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20they%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20stick%20that%20would%20analyse%20falls%20and%20provide%20a%20diagnosis.%20However%2C%20prohibitive%20costs%20forced%20them%20to%20rethink%20their%20approach.%20Since%20most%20seniors%20with%20gait%20issues%20already%20use%20a%20walking%20stick%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20develop%20a%20system%20that%20could%20be%20easily%20attached%20to%20any%20existing%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20product%20is%20a%20circuit%2C%20an%20attachment%20that%20can%20be%20fitted%20onto%20any%20stick%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahi.%20They%20spent%20about%20three%20months%20on%20research%20and%20designing%20their%20circuit%20with%20the%20help%20of%20their%20mentors%20at%20Omotec.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20they%20went%20through%20three%20prototypes%20and%20designs%20before%20coming%20up%20with%20their%20final%20retrofitted%20model%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20report%20states%20that%20falls%20are%20the%20second%20leading%20cause%20of%20unintentional%20injury%20deaths%20worldwide.%20It%20states%20that%20adults%20older%20than%2060%20years%20of%20age%20suffer%20the%20greatest%20number%20of%20fatal%20falls%20and%2037.3%20million%20falls%20every%20year%20require%20medical%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20420px)%20100vw%2C%20420px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20circuit%20generates%20real-time%20heat%20maps%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900.jpeg%20420w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900-300x193.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900-150x96.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362428%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20circuit%20generates%20real-time%20heat%20maps%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalkfit%20aims%20to%20be%20a%20preventive%20strategy%20for%20this%20massive%20problem.%20The%20duo%20worked%20with%20physiotherapists%20to%20understand%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiomechanics%20of%20falls%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Meghavi%20Desai%20Bhuptani%2C%20one%20of%20the%20physiotherapists%20who%20helped%20the%20students%2C%20says%20that%20the%20device%20can%20be%20very%20helpful%20for%20people%20who%20lack%20stability.%20%E2%80%9COsteoarthritis%2C%20caused%20due%20to%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%20your%20joints%20sets%20in%20after%20an%20age%20for%20almost%20everyone.%20We%20tend%20to%20recommend%20assistive%20devices%20for%20many%20such%20people%20post%2070%20or%20so%20to%20deal%20with%20imbalance.%20The%20mapping%20done%20by%20Walkfit%20can%20help%20users%20improve%20their%20gait%20and%20prevent%20falls.%20It%20will%20also%20be%20very%20useful%20for%20people%20who%20have%20suffered%20a%20stroke%20or%20have%20Parkinson%E2%80%99s%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreventing%20falls%20through%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalkfit%20comes%20with%20six%20pressure%20sensors%2C%20which%20are%20strategically%20placed%20on%20the%20stick%2C%20with%20two%20on%20the%20grip%20and%20four%20on%20the%20base.%20The%20system%20analyses%20the%20pressure%20exerted%20on%20the%20stick%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20determine%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20dependency%20on%20it.%20It%20can%20help%20diagnose%20potential%20health%20issues%20based%20on%20the%20pressure%20patterns%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnlXbceBCGtY%3Fenab